Class SkipGramRequestMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nd4j.parameterserver.distributed.messages.BaseVoidMessage
      • org.nd4j.parameterserver.distributed.messages.requests.SkipGramRequestMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, RequestMessage, TrainingMessage, VoidMessage

    public class SkipGramRequestMessage
extends BaseVoidMessage
implements TrainingMessage, RequestMessage
    This is batch message, describing simple SkipGram round We assume this message is created on Client, and passed to selected Shard Shard which received this message becomes a driver, which handles processing
